              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "heading": "ERR-1",
                "minimum_value": null,
                "maximum_value": null,
                "correlation_property": null
              },
              "free_text": [
                " The systematic uncertainty was  estimated  to",
                " be equal to 6 %."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The Ca-40(g,n)Ca-39 reaction cross section  has  been",
                " measured  with  tagged photons with energies ranging",
                " from 31.2 to 102 MeV, for neutron emission angles of",
                " 45,  60, 75, 90, and 135 deg. Exclusive differential",
                " cross sections for  the  Ca-40(g,n)  and  Ca-40(g,p)",
                " reactions  are  found  to be of a similar magnitude,",
                " but are not well predicted  by  recent  random-phase",
                " approximation   and  relativistic  direct  knock-out",
                " calculations.",
                "Exclusive differential cross section for the",
                " missing-energy  region  E-miss = -2.5 - 3.5 MeV were",
                " presented."
              ]
            }
          ],
